{"id":17736,"date":"2024-02-21T18:18:27","date_gmt":"2020-12-21T12:48:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=17736"},"modified":"2023-01-27T14:57:01","modified_gmt":"2023-01-27T09:27:01","slug":"modern-home-bar-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-home-bar-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Designing The Perfect Modern Home Bar For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Bold and stylish or elegant and minimalistic. Take your pick among the best <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-bar-design-ideas\/\"><em>home bar designs<\/em><\/a><em> from our inspirational guide<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An integral part of having a home is enjoying every corner of it, whether it is the warm sunlight on the balcony or a chic bar where you can unwind with a glass of Chardonnay in your pyjamas. Today,<strong> modern home bar designs<\/strong> are nothing like the \u201990s\u2019 lofty cabinets that take up space without adding an element of style. The statement accent of every home for a 20 or 30 something is their bar area. So, if you have decided to include a bar in your home entertainment area, you need these inspirational designs.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From a simple well-stocked liquor cabinet to professional set-ups, these modern home bar design ideas are both functional and elegant. To help you navigate through a maze of design options available today, we have chalked out some top home bar styles that compliment every home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Get Your Home Ready For Fun &amp; Safe House Parties | Home Bar Designs | Dining Room Designs\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/bLCm1LoBdCE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Creating the Perfect Terrace Garden and Bar Combination<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A terrace garden and bar combined as one is the perfect way to utilise space. Bring real restaurant bar vibes by swanking up the furniture and lights. Tucked away in the topmost area of the house, this entertainment zone has a spacious seating area beside the bar. To complete the bar atmosphere, pendant lights above the counter add an elaborate textural feel, while vibrant maroon bar chairs bring a sculptural layer of interest to the area.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180639\/modern-home-bar-design-picture.jpg\" alt=\"Modern home bar design on terrace with furniture and lights brings real restaurant bar vibe\" class=\"wp-image-17740\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180639\/modern-home-bar-design-picture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180639\/modern-home-bar-design-picture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180639\/modern-home-bar-design-picture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180639\/modern-home-bar-design-picture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>To enjoy a cosy nightcap all year long, cover the roof and enclose the area for your home bar with glass doors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Mini Bar Design For Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike the real mini bars, this design inspiration is best suited for small homes. This modern mini bar design for homes subtly separates the living area from the bar. The bar is perfect to host a small gang of friends. The wooden table complements the colour palette of the living area, while the white chairs help liven up the room\u2019s decor. Go ahead and decorate the shelf with chic statement bar accessories and one-of-a-kind glasses, making it easier to grab a drink when you\u2019re entertaining guests.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180651\/modern-mini-bar-design-for-home.jpg\" alt=\"Living cum dining area with a modern mini bar design for home.\" class=\"wp-image-17742\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180651\/modern-mini-bar-design-for-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180651\/modern-mini-bar-design-for-home-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180651\/modern-mini-bar-design-for-home-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180651\/modern-mini-bar-design-for-home-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Designed with functionality in mind, this home minibar design stands out in the living room and enhances its decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transitional Modern Home Bar Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>White is such an aesthetically pleasing colour for a home bar. It brings a cosy yet modern vibe to the area while infusing simple elements of minimalistic glam. While nothing about this modern home bar design screams out-of-the-box, yet the combination of black and white sets a perfect example of how a monotone colour scheme can add opulence to a space. Conveniently designed, this bar makes good use of the little corner in a home. The rustic white pendant lights over the bar countertop add just the right amount of style without stealing the limelight from the interiors. Keep the floors light and classic to match the wooden bar stools.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180657\/transitional-modern-home-mini-bar-design.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalistic modern home bar design for small space, a combination of black and white brings a cosy yet modern vibe.\" class=\"wp-image-17743\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180657\/transitional-modern-home-mini-bar-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180657\/transitional-modern-home-mini-bar-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180657\/transitional-modern-home-mini-bar-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180657\/transitional-modern-home-mini-bar-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>To infuse layers of finesse, use a wooden tray to place textural accents like a flower pot or a gold cocktail shaker on the counter<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Creating a Vintage and Rustic Home Bar Unit with a Modern Twist<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your home is blessed with ample space for a bar area, this vintage home bar unit is the way to go. With an already rustic vibe, it is important to keep clutter to a minimum. Make sure the bar area is the highlight by focusing on intriguing elements. The dusted brick red wall infuses more personality to the bar while the complementing brass lights create a texture-rich space. The use of warm browns and muted reds in this modern home bar design gives you all the more reason to celebrate special occasions at home.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180633\/modern-home-bar-design-ideas-with-vintage-touch.jpg\" alt=\"Modern home mini bar designed with wood and brick red wall infuses more personality to the bar brings vintage and rustic touch\" class=\"wp-image-17739\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180633\/modern-home-bar-design-ideas-with-vintage-touch.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180633\/modern-home-bar-design-ideas-with-vintage-touch-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180633\/modern-home-bar-design-ideas-with-vintage-touch-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180633\/modern-home-bar-design-ideas-with-vintage-touch-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Placing a wooden-framed mirror on the side will create the illusion of depth and make your home bar appear more spacious<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bold and Modern Home Bar Design Perfect for Entertaining<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike a traditional bar unit, this eclectic design is not for the faint-hearted. Matching the vibe of the house, this bold yet modern home bar design goes all out with a pop. This inspirational design shows that you do not need a massive room to create a space for your home bar. An impactful bar unit that almost blends with the living area yet stands out to create a wonderful entertaining space is what modern interiors are all about. The focus in this space is the high gloss blue table with a geometrical bar chair. Striking statement lights are the anchor that holds the vibrancy of the space together, while a solid matt black wall adds ambience to an otherwise peppy bar area.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180627\/modern-home-bar-design-for-small-space.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bar counter design for home blends with the living area yet stands out to create a wonderful entertaining space.\" class=\"wp-image-17738\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180627\/modern-home-bar-design-for-small-space.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180627\/modern-home-bar-design-for-small-space-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180627\/modern-home-bar-design-for-small-space-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/21180627\/modern-home-bar-design-for-small-space-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>When opting for vibrant home bar designs, play with contrasting home accents to infuse life into the space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Unleash your creative prowess by adding any of these modern home bar designs to your space. Depending on the size of your home, you can either jazz up a cosy nook or take over an entire room and style it up. If you are still looking for more inspirational ideas, reach out to us at DesignCafe, and we can help plan your home bar with you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>If you enjoyed reading about modern home bar designs, also explore:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-bar-counter-design\/\">Modern Bar Counter Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/home-bar-cabinet-designs\/\">Home Bar Cabinet Designs<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-bar-stools\/\">Kitchen Bar Stool Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                   